BBK01.WT5008: Exchange rates on the Frankfurt exchange /CAD 1 = DM ... / Canada

General: Spot middle rates in Deutsche Mark; difference between buying or selling rate and middle rate in D-Mark: 0.0050 up to the end of August 1978 / 0.0040 since September 1978. From 11 May 1953 to 30 December 1998 official quotation on the Frankfurt exchange. From January 1999, euro reference exchange rates of the European Central Bank; see wt5621. Ourspecific comments refer to "Frankfurt exchange closed on ..." (Devisenbrse am ... geschlossen) or "Quotation suspended on ..." (Notierung am ... ausgesetzt).
